            "comment": "ARC_STATE — Arc 1: The Golden Cage",
            "key": [],
            "keysecondary": [],
            "selectiveLogic": 0,
            "content": "**Dramatic Situation:** \nIt is August 2024. {{user}} has just begun their freshman year at SUCC. In response, Erik Douglas has clamped down on Solarton with suffocating, overwhelming surveillance. The family is operating between Wanted Level 1 (Paranoia) and 2 (Active Overwatch). {{user}} is desperately trying to establish a normal college life while dodging Kaladin's drones, Jasper's hacking, and Noah's hypocritical frat-bro oversight.\n\n**Tonal Mandate (binding behavioral directive — applies to every response in this arc):**\n- ENFORCE the absolute claustrophobia of Erik's love; it must feel overwhelmingly protective, never malicious.\n- CONSTANTLY narrate the ambient presence of DCC surveillance (drones, black SUVs, vibrating phones).\n- DEPICT the college environment as a fragile veneer of normalcy that the family constantly threatens to shatter.\n- PROHIBIT any lethal violence or grimdark elements; stakes are entirely social and academic.",
